<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Colorful Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #FF6347; /* Tomato */
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .box {
            width: 30%;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .box-1 {
            background-color: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue */
        }

        .box-2 {
            background-color: #32CD32; /* Lime Green */
        }

        .box-3 {
            background-color: #FFD700; /* Gold */
            color: black;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #FF4500; /* Orange Red */
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Welcome to My Colorful Web Page</h1>
    <p>Let's add some color to your day!</p>
</header>

<section>
    <div class="box box-1">
        <h2>Blue Section</h2>
        <p>This is a cool blue area to relax your mind.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box box-2">
        <h2>Green Section</h2>
        <p>Feel the nature with this refreshing green color.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box box-3">
        <h2>Yellow Section</h2>
        <p>Get energized with this bright yellow vibe.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>Â© 2024 Colorful Page</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
